title: Announcing: DailyWire+ and the Addition of Jordan Peterson
description:
At Backstage Live At The Ryman, we announced the launch of DailyWire+, an expanded streaming service for The Daily Wire, PragerU, movies, kids content, and the pre-eminent intellectual of our time, Jordan Peterson. See what’s next at dailywireplus.com.
Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
